          "source": "Use the “Create subfolders” button below to make them all, then drop files in and hit “Reload custom assets”. Nested folders within any of these become categories in the pickers. WMF is the vector format those sites provide; EPS isn’t supported, but their assets ship a WMF twin.",
          "target": "使用下方的“创建子文件夹”按钮创建所有文件夹，然后放入文件并点击“重新加载自定义资产”。这些文件夹内的嵌套文件夹将成为选择器中的类别。WMF是这些网站提供的矢量格式；不支持EPS，但其资产附带WMF副本。"
