        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "A reference to the shields, fields, tinctures, furs, ordinaries and charges this plugin offers — each with an example and a little history.",
          "target": "本插件提供的盾徽、纹章、纹饰、毛皮、普通纹章和图案的参考——每项均附有示例和简要历史。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "Inline code starting with this renders a shield, e.g. `heraldry:House Aldori`.",
          "target": "以此前缀开头的内联代码将渲染一个盾徽，例如 `heraldry:House Aldori`。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "Width in pixels for exported PNGs (height keeps the shield aspect).",
          "target": "导出 PNG 图片的宽度（像素），高度将保持盾徽的宽高比。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "Colour of the escutcheon outline.",
          "target": "盾徽轮廓的颜色。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "Where rolled names come from. The built-in generator is deterministic per seed; a custom script can call another plugin (Randomness, Dice Roller, …) or your own logic.",
          "target": "随机名称的来源。内置生成器基于种子确定性生成；自定义脚本可调用其他插件（如 Randomness、Dice Roller 等）或您自己的逻辑。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "Plugin whose API is bound to `api` in the script. e.g. \"randomness\", or \"obsidian-dice-roller\". Leave blank if your script does not need it.",
          "target": "其 API 绑定到脚本中 `api` 的插件。例如 \\\"randomness\\\" 或 \\\"obsidian-dice-roller\\\"。如果您的脚本不需要，请留空。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "JavaScript run to produce one name. In scope: app, api, seed. Return a string (async is fine). Falls back to the built-in generator on any error.",
          "target": "用于生成一个名称的 JavaScript 脚本。作用域内包含：app、api、seed。返回一个字符串（支持异步）。出错时将回退到内置生成器。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "Runs the script once and shows the result (or the error).",
          "target": "运行脚本一次并显示结果（或错误信息）。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "A provider was registered via setNameProvider() (e.g. from Templater). It takes precedence over the settings above until cleared.",
          "target": "已通过 setNameProvider() 注册了一个提供者（例如来自 Templater）。在清除之前，它将优先于上述设置。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "Frontmatter property a bare block/inline reads for a per-note seed. Set it once (e.g. from a template) to give a note random-but-consistent arms across the page.",
          "target": "裸块/内联代码读取的前置属性，用于获取每个笔记的种子。设置一次（例如通过模板）即可为笔记在整个页面上生成随机但一致的纹章。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "Insert heraldry blocks with controls off (adds a \"controls: false\" line) so a note shows a fixed coat of arms. Turn this off to insert rollable blocks with Reroll/Save/SVG/PNG buttons. You can always edit the line on an individual note.",
          "target": "插入纹章块时关闭控制（添加 \\\"controls: false\\\" 行），使笔记显示固定的纹章。关闭此选项可插入带有重新滚动/保存/SVG/PNG 按钮的可滚动块。您始终可以在单个笔记中编辑该行。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "Include the built-in fantasy charge pack (game-icons.net, CC BY 3.0 — see CREDITS).",
          "target": "包含内置奇幻图案包（来自 game-icons.net，CC BY 3.0 许可——详见 CREDITS）。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "Treat imported charges/ordinaries as silhouettes and recolour to the chosen tincture. Turn this off to keep original colours (recommended for full-colour clip-art such as heraldic achievements). Shields, fields and variations always keep their own artwork.",
          "target": "将导入的图案/普通纹章视为剪影，并重新着色为所选纹饰。关闭此选项可保留原始颜色（推荐用于全彩剪贴画，如纹章成就）。盾徽、纹章和变体始终保留其原始图案。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "Let the Roll tab use your imported assets — custom charges, ordinaries, shields, fields, variations and furs — alongside the built-ins. Off by default so rolls stay reproducible.",
          "target": "允许“滚动”选项卡使用您导入的资源——自定义图案、普通纹章、盾徽、纹章、变体和毛皮——与内置资源并用。默认关闭，以确保滚动结果可重现。"
        },
